reviews.name: Mira ayu Pratiwi
reviews.text:
ini review saya yg ke 2x nya. setelah sekian lama ngga laundry disini, krn sudah kepepet akhirnya mau ngga mau kesini. ternyata kondisinya hampir sama. totally dissapointed. kalau sdh ada msalah jadinya unprofessional dan cara bicara kurang menyenangkan.

dulu pernah bermasalah juga sama karyawan admin nya, sampai OWNER menghubungi saya dengan baik dan akhirnya berdamai. and now, it happens again.

summary:
1. pelayanan masih tetap kurang memuaskan. admin yang handle whatsapp chat sangat slow respon, di telpon sampai 10x tidak angkat telpon alasan ada customer padahal ditelpon saat sedang typing whatsapp-an dengan saya. unpredictablenya, saat angkat telpon, nada suara langsung tinggi menunjukkan kekesalan yang luar biasa.

2. ada cucian saya yang hilang, prosesnya lama. kalau ngga ditanya gmn updatenya, ngga ada info.

3. tidak ada update informasi laundryan sudah beres kalau tidak ditanya juga.

4. adminnya jauh lebih GALAK daripada customer. kayak sebuah bentakan krn nada suara tinggi, minta maaf sih tp suara nada tinggi, ngga ikhlas, terdengar terpaksa maafnya. customer tidak diberi kesempatan untuk bicara, dia terus yg bicara ngerocos ngga pake rem dan balik menyalahkan customer.

5. suka ngga nyambung antara pertanyaan dengan jawaban. sepertinya baca whatsapp message cuma selewatnya aja, ngga dibaca baik2 sehingga sering terjadi miscommunication.

to be honest, tempat laundry ini hasilnya cukup memuaskan, bekerja sesuai intruksi, hanya saja yang sangat disayangkan customer servicenya masih dibawah rata-rata. admin not capable to handling any type of clients. thank you
reviews.textTranslated:
This is my second review. After a long time without doing laundry here, I was forced to come here. It turned out to be almost the same situation. Totally disappointed. If there was a problem, the staff were unprofessional and the conversation was unpleasant.

I also had problems with the admin staff before, until the owner contacted me politely and finally made peace. And now, it happens again.

Summary:
1. The service remains unsatisfactory. The admin who handles WhatsApp chat is very slow to respond. I called up to 10 times without answering, claiming there was a customer, even though they were texting me on WhatsApp. What's more, when I answered the phone, my voice immediately became high-pitched, indicating extreme annoyance.

2. One of my laundry items was missing, and the process took a long time. If I didn't ask about it, I wouldn't get any updates.

3. There were no updates; the laundry was done without asking.

4. The admin was far more ANGRY than the customers. It sounded like a shout because of the high tone of voice. He apologized, but his tone was high, not sincere, and his apology sounded forced. The customer wasn't given a chance to speak; he just kept rambling, blaming the customer.

5. He often didn't connect questions with answers. He seemed to only read WhatsApp messages in passing, not reading them carefully, which often led to miscommunication.

To be honest, this laundry service is quite satisfactory, working according to instructions. It's just a shame the customer service is still below average. The admin isn't capable of handling any type of client. Thank you.
reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Halo Kak,

Terima kasih banyak atas kritik dan masukannya. Kami sangat menghargai waktu dan perhatian Kakak untuk menyampaikan hal ini kepada kami.

Terkait barang yang hilang, kami informasikan bahwa kaos kaki Kakak sudah berhasil ditemukan. Mohon maaf atas ketidaknyamanan yang sempat terjadi. Proses penelusuran memang membutuhkan waktu agar dapat dilakukan secara teliti dan menyeluruh, meskipun kami memahami hal tersebut terasa cukup lama bagi Kakak.

Selama lebih dari 7 tahun kami berdiri, kami terus berkomitmen untuk memperbaiki proses dan sistem layanan kami agar dapat memberikan pelayanan yang semakin baik dan memuaskan bagi seluruh pelanggan. Setiap ada komplain kerusakan ataupun kehilangan, selalu kami investigasi terlebih dahulu. jika memang terdapat kelalaian dari kami, selalu ada kompensasi penggantian. 

Masukan dari Kakak menjadi evaluasi berharga bagi kami untuk terus berkembang.
Sekali lagi kami mohon maaf atas ketidaknyamanan yang terjadi, dan terima kasih atas pengertian serta kepercayaan Kakak kepada layanan kami.

Hormat kami,
Tim Laundry

reviews.name: Muhammad Ruji
reviews.text: Sangat tidak bertanggung jawab dan mengecewakan. Laundry Bubbleklin sama sekali tidak menunjukkan profesionalisme. Ketika terjadi masalah, pihak laundry terkesan menghindar, lepas tangan, dan tidak memiliki niat menyelesaikan keluhan pelanggan. Respon buruk, komunikasi tidak jelas, dan pelayanan setelah pembayaran nyaris tidak ada. Janji manis di awal, tapi saat ada komplain justru menghilang. Waktu dan kepercayaan pelanggan benar-benar tidak dihargai. Pengalaman buruk, tidak layak direkomendasikan.
reviews.textTranslated: Extremely irresponsible and disappointing. Bubbleklin Laundry demonstrates a complete lack of professionalism. When problems arise, the laundry service seems evasive, hands-off, and has no intention of resolving customer complaints. Poor response, unclear communication, and virtually non-existent after-payment service. Sweet promises at the start, but when complaints arise, they disappear. Customers' time and trust are completely disrespected. A terrible experience, not worth recommending.
reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Terima kasih atas feedback yang Bapak/Ibu sampaikan. Kami mohon maaf apabila pengalaman yang dirasakan tidak sesuai harapan.

Namun setelah kami lakukan pengecekan pada data pelanggan dan riwayat transaksi, kami belum menemukan pelanggan atas nama Bapak/Ibu Muhammad Ruji, serta belum menemukan kejadian yang relevan dengan review ini. Oleh karena itu, kami khawatir terjadi kesalahpahaman atau ketidaksesuaian informasi.

Kami sangat terbuka dan bertanggung jawab untuk menyelesaikan setiap keluhan secara adil dan profesional. Agar permasalahan ini dapat ditindaklanjuti dengan tepat sesuai kejadian yang sebenarnya, kami mohon kesediaan Bapak/Ibu untuk menghubungi kami langsung melalui WhatsApp atau pesan Google Maps dengan menyertakan detail transaksi atas nama siapa, nomor WA yang terdaftar di sistem kami berapa, dan kronologi kejadiannya bagaimana.

Kami berharap dapat berkomunikasi secara langsung agar solusi terbaik dapat segera diberikan.

Hormat kami,
Manajemen BubbleKlin

reviews.textTranslated:
Untrustworthy. The first time I washed my clothes here, my hijab didn't look like it had been ironed and was still very wrinkled. I left my bag behind and had to send it back. Then, someone else's clothes ended up in my laundry. Does that mean they've mixed up their laundry?

Finally, I tried washing here a second time, after warning me not to repeat the same mistake. I thought it would go smoothly, but when I was about to send the laundry back to my address, the courier demanded I pay shipping. Even though I had already paid in full with LaundryKlin. The funny thing is, when I asked what they wanted, they told the courier to come back to them to get the money, but they didn't want to pay double the cost. Then the courier suggested I pay the money first and asked LaundryKlin to reimburse me. I told them, "Eeehhhhh, they're forcing me to make a deposit instead of a transfer?" So they forced me to go back to them with this incompetent service, laughing. Oh well, I felt sorry for the courier too. I was the one who paid the bill, and LaundryKlin still refused to refund me. I don't recommend this laundry service at all. üëé

reviews.text:
Awalnya gw milih laundry ini karna rating nya bagus trs ada laundry coin nya, pas dtg kok beda tp tetep ada laundry nya. Gw tny2 ternyata bnr laundry yg lama uda pindah akhirnya karna gw buru2 uda mlm dan disini KATANYA BISA EXPRESS akhirnya gw mau laundry dsni. Singkat cerita gw sekalian order galon pristin, Gw uda bayar sesuai sm harga yg dia ksh yaitu 15k per kg karna express. total 194.000 sm air galon gw bayar lah 204.000 biar kembalian lempeng 10rb, tbtb ibu ini chat gw kl kembalian nya lebih 40rb trs gw diminta bayar 33rb lagi, aneh. ga ngerti tuh gw asal muasalnya dr mana duit 33rb itu
Malam nya deal jam8/9 pagi diantar ternyata hujan. Oke gw maklumin gw tggu akhirnya berhenti itu hujan siang gw contact trs gada respon.

Sampe akhirnya sore dianter sm stafnya, dannnn yg bikin puasa gue hampir batal itu galon ga sekalian dianterin sementara gw nunggu uda dr pagi bener2 kacau üò§

Ga smpe disitu aja, tmpt pakaian kotor gw rusak, dan dia org gada responsibility apapun. Sumpah seKECEWA ITU GW LAUNDRY DISINI. KAPOKK GA AKAN LAGI .
reviews.textTranslated:
I initially chose this laundry because of its good ratings and coin laundry service. When I arrived, it was different, but they still had laundry. I asked around, but it turned out the old laundry had moved. I was in a hurry, as it was already late at night, and they said they offered express service, so I ended up doing laundry here. Long story short, I also ordered a gallon of Pristin. I paid the price they gave me, which was 15,000 per kg, for express service. The total was 194,000 and the gallon of water. I paid 204,000, so I got 10,000 in change. However, this lady texted me that her change was over 40,000, and then asked me to pay another 33,000. It was strange. I didn't understand where the 33,000 came from.
The night before, the deal was made at 8/9 a.m., and it was raining. I excused myself, but I waited until it finally stopped. It rained that afternoon, but I contacted her, but there was no response.

Finally, in the afternoon, the staff delivered it, and what almost broke my fast was that the gallon jug wasn't delivered while I'd been waiting all morning, a complete mess üò§

It didn't even stop there, my dirty clothes were ruined, and they didn't take any responsibility whatsoever. I swear I was SO DISAPPOINTED DOING LAUNDRY HERE. I WON'T REGRET IT AGAIN.

reviews.name: DP
reviews.text:
Red Flag since day one. Pelayanannya butuh perbaikan. Saya belum coba saja, sudah give up dengan service yang diberikan.

29 Des - saya hubungi nomor yang tertera di sini menanyakan apakah bisa pick up cucian? setelah sharing info mengenai pricelist dsb, ybs memberikan nomor contact untuk pick up dengan inisial KJ. Buat saya ini aneh karena customer journey-nya terputus, customer harus menghubungi lagi nomor lain, saya pun sempat bertanya tapi NO RESPOND.

30 Des - saya hubungi nomor yang diberikan (KJ), saya tanyakan bisa pick up jam berapa? dan endingnya ybs reply dengan "ke laundry lain saja" (walaupun diawali dengan kata maaf, tapi apakah bad service itu pantas dilakukan dengan bersampulkan kata maaf dan emoji üôèüèΩ ?)

Pelayanannya sangat buruk sekali, kenapa tidak dibuat announcement/heads up kepada customer H-7 atau H-2 bahwa laundry akan tutup/tidak melayani pick up dan share info lainnya yang memang customer perlu ketahui.

Kenapa customer dilempar sana-sini dan end up dengan tidak bisa melayani, just say it up front, saya juga pasti akan mengerti karena memang akhir tahun. Just be clear.

Saya tidak tau apa kualitas pekerja di area Maja memang sangat minim kualitas dan pengetahuannya mengenai service/hospitality, atau memang perlu refreshment/training dari owner laundry kepada staffnya mengenai customer journey yang lebih efisien dan efektif.

Selamat Tahun Baru, semoga ada perbaikan pelayanan ke depannya. God Bless.
reviews.textTranslated:
Red Flag since day one. The service needs improvement. I haven't even tried it yet, and I'm already giving up on the service.

December 29th - I called the number listed here and asked if laundry pickup was possible. After sharing information about the price list, etc., the person in question provided a contact number for pickup with the initials KJ. This struck me as odd because the customer journey was interrupted, requiring me to call another number. I even inquired, but received NO RESPONSE.

December 30th - I called the number provided (KJ) and asked what time pickup was possible. The person in question replied, "Let's go to another laundry." (Although it started with an apology, does bad service deserve an apology and a üôèüèΩ emoji?)

The service was terrible. Why wasn't there an announcement/heads up to customers seven or two days before that the laundry would be closed/not offering pickups, and share other information that customers really needed to know?

Why are customers being thrown around and ultimately unable to provide service? Just say it upfront. I'll definitely understand, since it's the end of the year. Just be clear.

I don't know if the quality of workers in the Maja area is truly lacking in service/hospitality skills and knowledge, or if the laundry owner really needs refresher training for his staff on a more efficient and effective customer journey.

Happy New Year, and hopefully, there will be improvements in service going forward. God bless.
